about.summary: An implementation of PEP 557: Data Classes

name: dataclasses
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.6" %}

package:
  name: dataclasses
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/d/dataclasses/dataclasses-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 6988bd2b895eef432d562370bb707d540f32f7360ab13da45340101bc2307d84

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: python -m pip install --no-deps --ignore-installed .

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.6,<3.7
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.6,<3.7

test:
  imports:
    - dataclasses

about:
  home: https://github.com/ericvsmith/dataclasses
  license: MIT
  summary: 'An implementation of PEP 557: Data Classes'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
